# Large files - use Git LFS or exclude
*.zip
*.map
*.gz
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.rar
*.7z

# Reference projects (external repos) — 仅跟踪 README + 下列 submodule 指针，见 reference/README.md
reference/*
!reference/README.md
!reference/reference_sourcemap/
reference/reference_sourcemap/*
!reference/reference_sourcemap/claude-code
!reference/reference_sourcemap/claude-code2
!reference/reference_sourcemap/leaked-claude-code
!reference/reference_sourcemap/open-claude-code

